    "html": "<section class=\"hero\">\n  <div class=\"hero-inner\">\n    <div class=\"badge\"><span class=\"dot\"></span> Sorteio ao Vivo – Resultados em Tempo Real</div>\n\n    <h1>Concorra a Prêmios<br/>Incríveis e <span>Mude sua Vida</span></h1>\n\n    <p class=\"sub\">Compre seus bilhetes agora e participe do maior sorteio online do Brasil. Chances reais, prêmios reais, ganhadores reais.</p>\n\n    <div class=\"cta-group\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn-main itu-accept\">🎟️ Comprar Bilhetes Agora</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn-sec\">Ver Prêmios →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"stats\">\n      <div class=\"stat\"><div class=\"stat-n\">R$50K</div><div class=\"stat-l\">Prêmio Principal</div></div>\n      <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n      <div class=\"stat\"><div class=\"stat-n\">12.480</div><div class=\"stat-l\">Participantes</div></div>\n      <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n      <div class=\"stat\"><div class=\"stat-n\">98%</div><div class=\"stat-l\">Satisfação</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #0f1117; }\n\n  .hero {\n    min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 0%, rgba(108,99,255,.25) 0%, transparent 60%),\n                radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 100%, rgba(245,158,11,.15) 0%, transparent 50%),\n                #0f1117;\n    padding: 3rem 1.5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .hero::before {\n    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;\n    background: url(\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%236c63ff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E\");\n    opacity: .5;\n  }\n  .hero-inner { max-width: 700px; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }\n\n  .badge {\n    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;\n    background: rgba(108,99,255,.15); border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.35);\n    color: #a78bfa; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 99px;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  }\n  .badge .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #a78bfa; border-radius: 50%; animation: blink 1.5s infinite; }\n  @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3} }\n\n  h1 {\n    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;\n    margin-bottom: 1.25rem; color: #f1f5f9;\n    text-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(108,99,255,.3);\n  }\n  h1 span { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#6c63ff,#f59e0b); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }\n\n  .sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }\n\n  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n\n  .btn-main {\n    padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 12px; border: none; cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #a855f7);\n    color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(108,99,255,.45);\n    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; text-decoration: none;\n    animation: pulse-btn 2.5s infinite;\n  }\n  .btn-main:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(108,99,255,.65); }\n  @keyframes pulse-btn { 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(108,99,255,.45)} 50%{box-shadow:0 8px 48px rgba(108,99,255,.75)} }\n\n  .btn-sec {\n    padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #2e3347; cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;\n    background: transparent; color: #94a3b8; transition: border-color .2s, color .2s; text-decoration: none;\n  }\n  .btn-sec:hover { border-color: #6c63ff; color: #e2e8f0; }\n\n  .stats { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; justify-content: center; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n  .stat { text-align: center; }\n  .stat-n { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #f1f5f9; }\n  .stat-l { font-size: .75rem; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; }\n  .divider { width: 1px; background: #2e3347; }",
