    "html": "<div class=\"card\">\n  <div class=\"tag\">⭐ Mais Popular</div>\n  <h2>Pacote 10 Bilhetes</h2>\n  <p class=\"desc\">Aumente suas chances de ganhar com nosso pacote mais vendido. Mais bilhetes, mais sorte!</p>\n\n  <div class=\"price-area\">\n    <div class=\"old-price\">De R$ 49,90</div>\n    <div class=\"price\">\n      <span class=\"currency\">R$</span>\n      <span class=\"amount\">29</span>\n      <span class=\"per\">,90</span>\n    </div>\n    <span class=\"savings\">🎉 Você economiza R$ 20,00</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <ul class=\"features\">\n    <li>10 bilhetes para o sorteio principal</li>\n    <li>Cadastro automático no sorteio</li>\n    <li>Confirmação por WhatsApp</li>\n    <li>Suporte prioritário</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <button class=\"btn itu-accept\">🎟️ Quero Este Pacote!</button>\n  <div class=\"safe\">🔒 Pagamento 100% seguro · PIX, Cartão e Boleto</div>\n</div>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; background: #0f1117; padding: 2rem; }\n\n  .card {\n    background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2e3347; border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 2rem; width: 100%; max-width: 380px;\n    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5);\n    position: relative; overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .card::before {\n    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6c63ff, #a855f7, #f59e0b);\n  }\n\n  .tag {\n    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;\n    background: rgba(108,99,255,.15); border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.3);\n    color: #a78bfa; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 99px;\n    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;\n  }\n\n  h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: #f1f5f9; margin-bottom: .5rem; }\n  .desc { color: #94a3b8; font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }\n\n  .price-area { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }\n  .old-price { color: #6b7280; font-size: .875rem; text-decoration: line-through; }\n  .price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 4px; }\n  .currency { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #10b981; }\n  .amount { font-size: 2.75rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f1f5f9; line-height: 1; }\n  .per { font-size: .8rem; color: #64748b; }\n\n  .savings {\n    display: inline-block; background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.3);\n    color: #10b981; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 6px;\n  }\n\n  .features { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }\n  .features li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: #cbd5e1; font-size: .875rem; }\n  .features li::before { content: '✓'; color: #10b981; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }\n\n  .btn {\n    width: 100%; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; border: none; cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #a855f7); color: #fff;\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(108,99,255,.4); transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;\n  }\n  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(108,99,255,.6); }\n\n  .safe { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; font-size: .72rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 1rem; }",
