    "category": "oferta",
    "categoryLabel": "Ofertas",
    "html": "<div class=\"card\">\n  <div class=\"card-header\">\n    <span class=\"ribbon\">🔥 Hot</span>\n    <span class=\"crown\">👑</span>\n    <div class=\"plan-name\">Premium VIP</div>\n    <h2>50 Bilhetes Elite</h2>\n    <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card-body\">\n    <div class=\"price-block\">\n      <span class=\"old\">R$ 199,90</span>\n      <div class=\"new-price\">\n        <span class=\"curr\">R$</span>\n        <span class=\"amt\">97</span>\n        <span class=\"cts\">,00</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"badge-off\">–51% OFF</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <ul class=\"features\">\n      <li><div class=\"check\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><polyline points=\"2 6 5 9 10 3\"/></svg></div>50 bilhetes exclusivos no sorteio</li>\n      <li><div class=\"check\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><polyline points=\"2 6 5 9 10 3\"/></svg></div>Acesso ao grupo VIP de ganhadores</li>\n      <li><div class=\"check\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><polyline points=\"2 6 5 9 10 3\"/></svg></div>Notificação em tempo real via WhatsApp</li>\n      <li><div class=\"check\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><polyline points=\"2 6 5 9 10 3\"/></svg></div>Suporte 24h dedicado</li>\n      <li><div class=\"check\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><polyline points=\"2 6 5 9 10 3\"/></svg></div>Bilhetes para o sorteio bônus exclusivo</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <button class=\"btn itu-accept\">👑 Quero o Pacote VIP Agora!</button>\n    <div class=\"safe\">🔒 Garantia de 7 dias · Pagamento seguro</div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; background: #0f1117; padding: 2rem; }\n\n  .card {\n    width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.6);\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  /* Gradiente de fundo premium */\n  .card-header {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a3d 0%, #2d1b69 100%);\n    padding: 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .card-header::before {\n    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -60px; right: -60px;\n    width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%;\n    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(168,85,247,.4), transparent);\n  }\n  .card-header::after {\n    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -40px; left: -40px;\n    width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%;\n    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,158,11,.2), transparent);\n  }\n\n  .crown { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; display: block; }\n  .plan-name { font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .15em; color: #a78bfa; }\n  h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; margin: .25rem 0 .5rem; }\n  .stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: .9rem; }\n\n  .ribbon {\n    position: absolute; top: 20px; right: -30px; transform: rotate(45deg);\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ef4444);\n    color: #fff; font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 6px 40px;\n    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.3);\n  }\n\n  .card-body { background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2e3347; border-top: none; padding: 1.75rem; }\n\n  .price-block { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n  .old { text-decoration: line-through; color: #6b7280; font-size: .875rem; }\n  .new-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 3px; }\n  .curr { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #f59e0b; }\n  .amt { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f1f5f9; line-height: 1; }\n  .cts { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #f1f5f9; align-self: flex-start; margin-top: 4px; }\n  .badge-off { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444,#dc2626); color: #fff; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 8px; }\n\n  .features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }\n  .features li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; color: #cbd5e1; font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.5; }\n  .check { width: 18px; height: 18px; background: linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#059669); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }\n  .check svg { width: 10px; height: 10px; stroke: #fff; stroke-width: 3; fill: none; }\n\n  .btn {\n    width: 100%; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; border: none; cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 800;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ef4444); color: #fff;\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(245,158,11,.4); transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;\n    letter-spacing: .02em; animation: glow 2.5s infinite;\n  }\n  @keyframes glow { 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(245,158,11,.4)} 50%{box-shadow:0 6px 40px rgba(245,158,11,.7)} }\n  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }\n\n  .safe { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; font-size: .72rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 1rem; }",
