    "html": "<div class=\"overlay\">\n  <div class=\"popup\" style=\"position:relative\">\n    <div class=\"top-bar\">\n      <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#fff\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2a10 10 0 100 20A10 10 0 0012 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z\"/></svg>\n      <span>Espere! Antes de ir, veja esta oferta...</span>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"close-btn itu-close\" onclick=\"document.querySelector('.overlay').remove()\">✕</button>\n    <div class=\"body\">\n      <div class=\"emoji-wrap\">🎁</div>\n      <div class=\"content\">\n        <h2>Última Chance de<br/>Garantir Seus Bilhetes!</h2>\n        <p>Preparamos um desconto especial de saída exclusivo para você. Esta oferta desaparece quando você sair.</p>\n        <div class=\"price-row\">\n          <span class=\"old\">R$ 49,90</span>\n          <span class=\"new\">R$ 19,90</span>\n          <span class=\"tag\">–60% OFF</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"btns\">\n          <button class=\"btn-main itu-accept\">🎟️ Sim! Quero os Bilhetes com Desconto</button>\n          <button class=\"btn-no itu-reject\">Não obrigado, prefiro pagar mais depois.</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; background: #0f1117; }\n\n  .overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,.82); display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center; padding: 1.5rem; backdrop-filter: blur(4px); z-index: 100; }\n\n  .popup {\n    background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2e3347; border-radius: 20px 20px 20px 20px;\n    max-width: 460px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 -20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.5);\n    animation: slide-up .5s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);\n  }\n  @keyframes slide-up { from{transform:translateY(100px);opacity:0} to{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1} }\n\n  .top-bar { background: #ef4444; padding: 8px 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }\n  .top-bar span { color: #fff; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700; }\n  .top-bar svg { animation: blink 1.5s infinite; }\n  @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3} }\n\n  .body { padding: 1.75rem; display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start; }\n  .emoji-wrap { font-size: 3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }\n  .content h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #f1f5f9; margin-bottom: .375rem; }\n  .content p { font-size: .875rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }\n\n  .price-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }\n  .old { font-size: .875rem; color: #6b7280; text-decoration: line-through; }\n  .new { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f1f5f9; }\n  .tag { background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.3); color: #10b981; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px; }\n\n  .btns { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .5rem; }\n  .btn-main {\n    padding: 13px 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: none; cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 800;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#059669); color: #fff;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(16,185,129,.35); transition: transform .15s;\n  }\n  .btn-main:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }\n  .btn-no { background: none; border: none; color: #6b7280; font-size: .78rem; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; }\n  .btn-no:hover { color: #94a3b8; }\n\n  .close-btn { position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 14px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); border: none; color: #94a3b8; width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; font-size: .875rem; }",
