    "category": "premios",
    "categoryLabel": "Premios",
    "html": "<div class=\"card\">\n  <div class=\"card-header\">\n    <span class=\"trophy\">🏆</span>\n    <div class=\"prize-tag\">🥇 Prêmio Principal</div>\n    <h2>Chevrolet Onix 0km</h2>\n    <p class=\"prize-desc\">Modelo 2024, completo, cor prata</p>\n    <div class=\"value-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"value-label\">Valor do Prêmio</div>\n      <div class=\"value\">R$ 79.990,00</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card-body\">\n    <ul class=\"details\">\n      <li><span class=\"icon\">📅</span>Sorteio: 30 de Junho de 2025</li>\n      <li><span class=\"icon\">🎟️</span>1 bilhete = 1 chance de ganhar</li>\n      <li><span class=\"icon\">✅</span>Registrado na Caixa Econômica</li>\n      <li><span class=\"icon\">🔒</span>100% seguro e transparente</li>\n    </ul>\n    <button class=\"btn itu-accept\">🎟️ Quero Concorrer a Este Prêmio!</button>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; background: #0f1117; padding: 2rem; }\n\n  .card {\n    background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2e3347; border-radius: 24px;\n    max-width: 380px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.5);\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  .card-header {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a3d 0%, #2d1b69 100%);\n    padding: 2rem; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .card-header::before {\n    content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;\n    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(245,158,11,.2), transparent 60%);\n  }\n\n  .trophy { font-size: 4rem; display: block; margin-bottom: .5rem; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  @keyframes float { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(-8px)} }\n\n  .prize-tag {\n    display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#ef4444);\n    color: #fff; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: .1em; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: .75rem;\n  }\n  h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; margin-bottom: .25rem; }\n  .prize-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); font-size: .875rem; }\n\n  .value-wrap {\n    background: rgba(245,158,11,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.3);\n    border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; margin: 1.25rem 0 0;\n  }\n  .value-label { font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); margin-bottom: 2px; }\n  .value { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f59e0b; }\n\n  .card-body { padding: 1.5rem; }\n  .details { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }\n  .details li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: .875rem; color: #cbd5e1; }\n  .details li .icon { font-size: 1rem; }\n\n  .btn {\n    width: 100%; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; border: none; cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#ef4444); color: #fff;\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(245,158,11,.4); transition: transform .2s;\n    animation: glow-btn 2.5s infinite;\n  }\n  @keyframes glow-btn { 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(245,158,11,.4)}50%{box-shadow:0 6px 40px rgba(245,158,11,.7)} }\n  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }",
