    "category": "premios",
    "categoryLabel": "Premios",
    "html": "<div class=\"section\">\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-label\">🏆 Premiação Total</div>\n    <h2>Mais de R$ 150.000 em Prêmios</h2>\n    <p class=\"sub\">Confira todos os prêmios do nosso mega sorteio</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"prizes-list\">\n    <div class=\"prize-row first\">\n      <div class=\"medal\">🥇</div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"position\">1º Lugar</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-name\">Chevrolet Onix 0km</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-detail\">Modelo 2024, completo, cor prata</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"prize-value\"><div class=\"value\">R$ 79.990</div><div class=\"value-label\">Valor estimado</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-row second\">\n      <div class=\"medal\">🥈</div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"position\">2º Lugar</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-name\">R$ 30.000 em Dinheiro</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-detail\">Transferência PIX na hora</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"prize-value\"><div class=\"value\">R$ 30.000</div><div class=\"value-label\">Pix imediato</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-row third\">\n      <div class=\"medal\">🥉</div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"position\">3º Lugar</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-name\">Moto Honda CG 160</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-detail\">0km, emplacada</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"prize-value\"><div class=\"value\">R$ 14.000</div><div class=\"value-label\">Valor estimado</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-row\">\n      <div class=\"medal\">🎁</div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"position\">4º ao 10º Lugar</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-name\">R$ 2.000 cada</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-detail\">7 ganhadores via PIX</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"prize-value\"><div class=\"value\">R$ 14.000</div><div class=\"value-label\">Total</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-row\">\n      <div class=\"medal\">🍀</div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"position\">Sorteio Instantâneo</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-name\">100 Prêmios de R$ 100</div>\n        <div class=\"prize-detail\">A cada bilhete comprado</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"prize-value\"><div class=\"value\">R$ 10.000</div><div class=\"value-label\">Total</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #0f1117; padding: 2rem; }\n\n  .section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }\n  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }\n  .section-label { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .15em; color: #f59e0b; margin-bottom: .5rem; }\n  h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f1f5f9; }\n  .sub { color: #94a3b8; font-size: .875rem; margin-top: .375rem; }\n\n  .prizes-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem; }\n\n  .prize-row {\n    background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2e3347; border-radius: 14px;\n    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.25rem;\n    transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s; cursor: default;\n  }\n  .prize-row:hover { border-color: rgba(245,158,11,.4); transform: translateX(4px); }\n  .prize-row.first { border-color: rgba(245,158,11,.3); background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(245,158,11,.06), #1a1d27); }\n  .prize-row.second { border-color: rgba(203,213,225,.15); background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(203,213,225,.04), #1a1d27); }\n  .prize-row.third { border-color: rgba(180,83,9,.2); background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(180,83,9,.04), #1a1d27); }\n\n  .medal { font-size: 1.75rem; flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; text-align: center; }\n  .position { font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; color: #64748b; }\n  .prize-info { flex: 1; }\n  .prize-name { font-weight: 700; color: #f1f5f9; font-size: .95rem; margin-bottom: 2px; }\n  .prize-detail { font-size: .78rem; color: #94a3b8; }\n\n  .prize-value { text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }\n  .value { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: #f59e0b; }\n  .prize-row.second .value { color: #cbd5e1; }\n  .prize-row.third .value { color: #b45309; }\n  .prize-row:not(.first):not(.second):not(.third) .value { color: #6c63ff; }\n  .value-label { font-size: .65rem; color: #64748b; }",
