    "category": "premios",
    "categoryLabel": "Premios",
    "html": "<div class=\"showcase\">\n  <h2>🏆 Prêmios do Sorteio</h2>\n  <p class=\"sub\">Concorra a todos estes prêmios incríveis</p>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <div class=\"prize-card highlighted\">\n      <span class=\"prize-emoji\">🚗</span>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-name\">Chevrolet Onix 0km</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-val\">R$ 79.990</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-pos\">1º Lugar</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-card\">\n      <span class=\"prize-emoji\">💰</span>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-name\">Dinheiro no PIX</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-val\">R$ 30.000</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-pos\">2º Lugar</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-card\">\n      <span class=\"prize-emoji\">🏍️</span>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-name\">Moto Honda CG</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-val\">R$ 14.000</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-pos\">3º Lugar</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-card\">\n      <span class=\"prize-emoji\">📱</span>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-name\">iPhone 15 Pro</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-val\">R$ 8.999</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-pos\">4º Lugar</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-card\">\n      <span class=\"prize-emoji\">🖥️</span>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-name\">Smart TV 65\"</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-val\">R$ 4.500</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-pos\">5º Lugar</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prize-card\">\n      <span class=\"prize-emoji\">🎁</span>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-name\">+100 Prêmios</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-val\">Até R$ 1.000</div>\n      <div class=\"prize-card-pos\">Sorteio Instantâneo</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "css": "*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #0f1117; padding: 2rem; }\n\n  .showcase { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }\n  h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f1f5f9; margin-bottom: .375rem; }\n  .sub { color: #94a3b8; font-size: .875rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }\n\n  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }\n  @media(max-width:560px){ .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }\n\n  .prize-card {\n    background: #1a1d27; border: 1px solid #2e3347; border-radius: 16px;\n    padding: 1.5rem 1rem; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\n    transition: transform .2s, border-color .2s;\n  }\n  .prize-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: rgba(108,99,255,.4); }\n  .prize-card.highlighted {\n    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e1450, #2d1b69);\n    border-color: rgba(108,99,255,.5);\n    grid-column: span 1;\n  }\n  .prize-card.highlighted::before {\n    content:'🔥 Em destaque';\n    position:absolute; top:10px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);\n    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6c63ff,#a855f7);\n    color:#fff; font-size:.6rem; font-weight:800; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:99px;\n    white-space:nowrap; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em;\n  }\n\n  .prize-emoji { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; margin-top: .5rem; display: block; }\n  .prize-card.highlighted .prize-emoji { animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }\n  @keyframes float { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(-6px)} }\n\n  .prize-card-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: .875rem; color: #f1f5f9; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n  .prize-card-val { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; color: #f59e0b; }\n  .prize-card-pos { font-size: .68rem; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; margin-top: 4px; }",
